name: .WB0 File Extension
summary: Learn about .WB0 files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Picture file format used by Webshots Desktop Connect, a program used to share, organize, and view pictures; contains a picture image used by Webshots to help users organize their pictures.

content: NOTE: Webshots Desktop Connect was formerly known as Webshots Desktop and was owned by AG Interactive before being acquired by Threefold Photos in 2012.
